ry%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESen.%20Bob%20Casey%20wants%20to%20chip%20away%20at%20wealth%20inequality%20and%20set%20up%20kids%20to%20be%20able%20to%20build%20wealth.%20His%20proposal%3A%20A%20%26quot%3B401Kids%26quot%3B%20savings%20account%20established%20for%20every%20kid%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECasey%2C%20a%20Democrat%20from%20Pennsylvania%2C%20is%20introducing%20legislation%20that%20would%20create%20Child%20Savings%20Accounts%20nationwide.%20Under%20Casey's%20legislation%2C%20savings%20accounts%20would%20be%20established%20for%20every%20kid%20in%20the%20country%3B%20they'd%20operate%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-a-529-plan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E529%20plans%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20state-run%20accounts%20used%20to%20save%20for%20educational%20costs.%20Like%20529s%2C%20they'd%20be%20managed%20by%20state%20treasurers.%20When%20kids%20turn%2018%2C%20they'd%20be%20able%20to%20use%20the%20money%20on%20post-secondary%20education%2C%20starting%20a%20small%20business%2C%20buying%20a%20home%20%E2%80%94%20or%20even%20sock%20it%20away%20for%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lack%20of%20income%20means%20you%20can't%20get%20by%2C%20but%20a%20lack%20of%20wealth%20means%20you%20can't%20get%20ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20Casey%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAs%20American%20families%20grapple%20with%20rising%20costs%2C%20they%20deserve%20a%20way%20to%20save%20not%20just%20for%20their%20future%2C%20but%20for%20their%20children's%20future.%20My%20401Kids%20Savings%20Act%20would%20provide%20every%20child%20in%20this%20Nation%20with%20the%20cushion%20they%20need%20to%20take%20risks%20and%20pursue%20opportunities%20to%20create%20generational%20wealth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParents%2C%20nonprofits%2C%20and%20other%20family%20members%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20child%20%E2%80%94%20would%20be%20able%20to%20contribute%2