20Seat%26quot%3B%3A%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20Slams%20Congress%2C%20Sets%20A%20Condition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20remarks%20that%20indicated%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20troubles%20in%20Bengal%20are%20far%20from%20over%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20today%20said%20the%20Congress%20must%20part%20ways%20with%20the%20CPM%20if%20they%20want%20any%20tie-up%20with%20her%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20had%20rejected%20the%20Trinamool's%20offer%20for%20two%20seats%20during%20seat-sharing%20negotiations%20and%20now%20she%20%26quot%3Bwon't%20give%20a%20single%20seat%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPM%20has%20physically%20attacked%20me%20on%20several%20occasions%20in%20the%20past.%20I%20was%20mercilessly%20beaten%20up.%20I%20am%20alive%20only%20because%20of%20the%20blessings%20of%20my%20well-wishers.%20I%20can%20never%20forgive%20the%20Left%2C%20I%20can%20never%20forgive%20the%20CPM.%20So%20those%20who%20are%20with%20CPM%20today%2C%20they%20can%20also%20be%20with%20the%20BJP.%20I%20won't%20forgive%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20a%20gathering%20in%20Malda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20her%20remarks%20came%20on%20a%20day%20when%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20re-entered%20Bengal%20after%20its%20Bihar%20leg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20told%20congress%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20single%20MLA%20in%20the%20assembly.%20We%20will%20give%20you%20two%20parliamentary%20seats%20and%20we%20will%20make%20sure%20your%20candidate%20wins.%20But%20they%20want%20more%20seats%2C%20so%20I%20told%20them%20I%20won't%20give%20you%20a%20single%20seat%20until%20u%20leave%20the%20company%20of%20the%20Left%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPM%20has%20earlier%20ruled%20out%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Trinamool.%20Back%20in%20June%2C%20CPM%20general%20secretary%20Sitaram%20Yechury%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMamata%20Banerjee%20and%20the%20CPM%20will%20not%20happen.%20There%20will%20be%20secular%20parties%20along%20with%20the%20Left%20and%20the%20Congress%20in%20Bengal%20which%20will%20fight%20against%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20TMC%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeat-sharing%20talks%20between%20the%20Trinamool%20and%20Congress%20hit%20a%20roadblock%20a%20week%20back%20when%20Ms%20Banerjee%20announced%20that%20her%20party%20will%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20alone%20and%20any%20decision%20on%20an%20alliance%20will%20be%20taken%20after%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20blamed%20Congress's%20hard%20bargaining%20and%20strong%20remarks%20by%20its%20state%20chief%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20for%20Ms%20Banerjee%20for%20the%20situation.%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20had%20argued%20that%20the%20two%20seats%20being%20offered%20to%20the%20Congress%20were%20the%20party's%20strongholds%20anyway%2C%20and%20said%20the%20Congress%20is%20equipped%20to%20win%20elections%20on%20its%20own.%20In%20a%20personal%20attack%20on%20the%20Trinamool%20supremo%2C%20he%20had%20called%20her%20an%20%26quot%3Bopportunist%26quot%3B%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20outburst%2C%20the%20Congress%20leadership%20swiftly%20moved%20into%20damage%20control%20and%20said%20it%20cannot%20imagine%20an%20INDIA%20bloc%20without%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%20The%20Trinamool%20chief's%20remarks%20today%20suggest%20that%20the%20issue%20is%20nowhere%20close%20to%20being%20sorted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20is%20just%20one%20among%20the%20regional%20forces%20locked%20in%20a%20tug-of-war%20with%20the%20Congress%20over%20seat-sharing.%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20and%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20has%20said%20they%20are%20preparing%20to%20contest%20all%2013%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20has%20announced%2016%20candidates%20amid%20seat-sharing%20talks.