he%20most%20desirable%20places%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20that's%20why%20Googlers%20are%20so%20disturbed%20by%20this%20new%20way%20of%20doing%20business.%20While%20the%20recent%20layoffs%20are%20not%20the%20first%20in%20Google's%20history%20%E2%80%94%20it%20made%20a%206%25%20cut%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20they%20do%20signal%20that%20the%20days%20of%20treating%20employees%20like%20family%20are%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20this%20comes%20down%20to%20breaking%20an%20%26quot%3Bunwritten%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bpsychological%26quot%3B%20contract%20employees%20have%20with%20companies%2C%20Ben%20Hardy%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20organizational%20behavior%20at%20London%20Business%20School%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccess%20to%20various%20perks%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20%26quot%3Bpsychological%20safety%26quot%3B%20may%20not%20be%20explicitly%20stated%20in%20an%20employee's%20contract%2C%20but%20Google%20workers%20have%20come%20to%20expect%20these%20things%20because%20of%20the%20company's%20reputation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHardy%20added%20that%20the%20first%20round%20of%20layoffs%20breached%20this%20unwritten%20contract%20with%20employees%2C%20but%20the%20latest%20cuts%20might%20have%20changed%20it%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20they're%20taking%20it%20harder%20is%20that%20it's%20not%20a%20feeling%20of%20'Google%20doing%20what%20Google%20has%20to%20do.'%20For%20employees%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20maybe%20they%20fundamentally%20got%20this%20wrong%20about%20that%20organization.%20Maybe%20this%20isn't%20the%20place%20they%20thought%20it%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EUnintended%20consequences%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20will%20likely%20continue%20to%20reshape%20its%20business%20to%20adapt%20to%20market%20demands%2C%20meaning%20a%20workplace%20culture%20defined%20by%20rounds%20of%20layoffs%20may%20be%20the%20new%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoogle%20was%20known%20for%20a%20long%20time%20as%20being%20the%20top%20company%20%E2%80%94%20everybody%20wanted%20to%20work%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Thomas%20Roulet%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20organizational%20sociology%20and%20leadership%20at%20the%20Univerity%20of%20Cambridge%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20it's%20flipped%20partly%20because%20of%20the%20rise%20of%20generative%20AI%2C%20which%20is%20really%20threatening%20some%20of%20the%20core%20businesses%20at%20Google.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWorking%20for%20Google%20is%20just%20not%20as%20sexy%20and%20exciting%20as%20it%20used%20to%20be%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20laid%20off%20anytime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20layoffs%20and%20changing%20culture%20at%20Google%20could%20come%20back%20to%20haunt%20the%20company%20in%20more%20ways%20than%20one%2C%20causing%20trouble%20for%20retention%20and%20recruitment%2C%20Roulet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20start%20laying%20off%20people%2C%20the%20people%20who%20are%20left%20behind%20have%20lower%20trust.%20They%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20sabotaging%20their%20own%20culture%20and%20losing%20some%20of%20their%20top%20employees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'Not%20just%20robots'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20has%20created%20an%20environment%20where%20its%20employees%20have%20a%20voice%20and%20are%20largely%20unafraid%20to%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGooglers%20are%20also%20unique%20in%20their%20autonomy%2C%20Roulet%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20just%20robots%20%E2%80%94%20they%20actually%20have%20their%20own%20thoughts%20about%20what%20the%20firm%20should%20be%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20company's%20long%20history%20of%20internal%20activism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20free%20food%20and%20ski%20trips%2C%20Google's%20also%20worked%20hard%20to%20cultivate%20a%20culture%20of%20creativity.%20The%20psychological%20effects%20of%20ongoing%20layoffs%20may%20also%20affect%20how%20employees%20do%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20space%20to%20create%20and%20innovate%20is%20completely%20at%20odds%20with%20the%20risk%20of%20layoffs.%20Workers%20will%20not%20be%20as%20creative%2C%20and%20how%20they%20carry%20out%20their%20jobs%20will%20be%20more%20conservative%2C%26quot%3B%20Roulet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-sexy-exciting-layoffs-prove-golden-era-over-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706697255000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b7d1246c8f0a134f7ab998%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-sexy-exciting-layoffs-prove-golden-era-over-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google's%20latest%20round%20of%20layoffs%20has%20heightened%20fears%20about%20its%20impact%20on%20creativity%20and%20innovation%20at%20the%20company%2C%20experts%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bnolan%40insider.com%20(Beatrice%20Nolan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-sexy-exciting-layoffs-prove-golden-era-over-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli's%20brother%20clears%20rumours%20about%20his%20mother's%20health%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706697129000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107291933%2Cimgsize-52820.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fvirat-kohlis-brother-clears-rumours-about-his-mothers-health%2Farticleshow%2F107291974.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat's%20elder%20brother%20clarified%20on%20his%20official%20Instagram%20handle%20that%20their%20mother%20is%20'absolutely%20fit%20and%20fine'.%20He%20urged%20everyone%20to%20refrain%20from%20spreading%20un