a%20Foxx%2C%20R-N.C.%2C%20attends%20a%20news%20conference%20featuring%20remarks%20by%20college%20students%20about%20antisemitism%20on%20college%20campuses%2C%20in%20the%20U.S.%20Capitol%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20December%205%2C%202023.%3Cp%3ETom%20Williams%2FCQ-Roll%20Call%2C%20Inc%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHouse%20Republicans%20are%20reviewing%20a%20bill%20that%20would%20overhaul%20the%20student-loan%20system.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20proposes%20limits%20on%20the%20education%20secretary%20for%20getting%20new%20forms%20of%20relief%20to%20borrowers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDemocrats%20introduced%20their%20own%20package%20to%20address%20student%20debt%2C%20but%20it's%20unlikely%20to%20advance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHouse%20Republicans%20are%20moving%20forward%20with%20a%20bill%20that%20could%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20student-loan%20borrowers%20to%20get%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-who-qualifies-latest-round-biden-debt-cancellation-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20forms%20of%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20House%20education%20committee%20is%20moving%20forward%20with%20review%20and%20debate%20over%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedworkforce.house.gov%2Fnews%2Fdocumentsingle.aspx%3FDocumentID%3D409975%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECollege%20Cost%20Reduction%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20introduced%20by%20GOP%20chair%20of%20the%20committee%20Virginia%20Foxx%20in%20early%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20outlines%20a%20range%20of%20priorities%2C%20including%20strengthened%20guidelines%20for%20college%20accreditation%2C%20implementing%20caps%20on%20certain%20forms%20of%20financial%20aid%2C%20and%20limiting%20the%20education%20secretary's%20authority%20to%20implement%20new%20repayment%20and%20relief%20programs%20for%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Foxx%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20there%20is%20bipartisan%20agreement%20that%20student%20debt%20in%20the%20country%20is%20spiraling%2C%20there's%20likely%20to%20be%20some%20Democratic%20pushback%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20her%20proposals%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20efforts%20to%20shorten%20student-loan%20repayment%20for%20many%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStudent%20loan%20debt%20is%20skyrocketing%2C%20and%20completion%20rates%20are%20plummeting.%20There's%20bipartisan%20agreement%20that%20lasting%20reforms%20are%20needed%20to%20correct%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20Foxx%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20said%20her%20plan%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20responsible%20alternative%20to%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20free%20college%20agenda%2C%20which%20is%20placing%20an%20enormous%20burden%20on%20students%20and%20taxpayers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20bill%20offers%20reforms%20to%20the%20Higher%20Education%20Act%20that%20will%20lower%20college%20costs%2C%20rein%20in%20executive%20overreach%2C%20and%20prevent%20colleges%20from%20endlessly%20raising%20the%20cost%20of%20tuition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawmakers%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20aisle%20have%20offered%20solutions%20to%20combat%20the%20student%20debt%20crisis%2C%20but%20there's%20disagreement%20on%20the%20best%20way%20to%20do%20so.%20The%20Education%20Department%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-what-is-next-biden-debt-cancellation-relief-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimplementing%20student-debt%20relief%20for%20borrowers%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-supreme-court-strikes-down-debt-cancellation-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruck%20down%20Biden's%20first%20attempt%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Along%20with%20that%20relief%2C%20the%20department%20has%20also%20carried%20out%20targeted%20batches%20of%20forgiveness%20through%20account%20adjustments%2C%20along%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-student-loan-forgiveness-early-income-driven-repayment-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eupcoming%20relief%20through%20its%20new%20SAVE%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20many%20Republicans%20have%20opposed%20the%20department's%20efforts%20to%20make%20new%20repayment%20plans%20and%20implement%20streamlined%20processes%20for%20relief%2C%20saying%20the%20burden%20of%20debt%20forgiveness%20falls%20on%20taxpayers.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHere's%20how%20Foxx's%20legislation%20would%20change%20things%20for%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20the%20GOP%20bill%20means%20for%20student-loan%20borrowers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaps%20student%20borrowing.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAccording%20to%20the%20bill's%20fact%20sheet%2C%20the%20bill%20would%20cap%20student-loan%20borrowing%20at%20%2450%2C000%20for%20undergraduate%20students%2C%20%24100%2C000%20for%20graduate%20students%2C%20and%20%24150%2C000%20for%20students%20in%20graduate%20professional%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20would%20also%20sunset%20the%20grad%20and%20parent%20PLUS%20loan%20programs%2C%20which%20are%20loans%20graduate%20students%20and%20parents%20can%20take%20out%20in%20their%20own%20names%20to%20cover%20up%20to%20the%20full%20cost%20of%20attendance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeet-single-mom-student-debt-plus-loans-set-to-double-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20spoken%20to%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20have%20struggled%20to%20repay%20their%20PLUS%20loans%20due%20to%20the%20high-interest%20rates%20that%20can%20leave%20them%20with%20balances%20far%20larger%20than%20what%20they%20originally%20borrowed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStreamlines%20repayment%20plans.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20student-loan%20repayment%20in%20particular%2C%20the%20legislation%20aims%20to%20put%20constraints%20on%20the%20Education%20Department's%20ability%20to%20implement%20new%20programs.%20Specifically%2C%20the%20bill%20would%20establish%20two%20types%20of%20repayment%20plans%3A%20a%2010-year%20%26quot%3Bmortgage-style%26quot%3B%20plan%20and%20an%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELimits%20debt%20relief.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20fact%20sheet%20said%20the%20bill%20would%20prohibit%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Secretary%20from%20creating%20new%20repayment%20plans%20and%20from%20modifying%20an%20existing%20repayment%20plan%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20increases%20costs%20to%20the%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20would%20also%20repeal%20the%20Education%20Department's%20efforts%20to%20streamline%20the%20process%20for%20borrowers%20who%20say%20they%20were%20defrauded%20by%20their%20schools%20to%20get%20relief%2C%20along%20with%20rules%20that%20would%20ensure%20debt%20relief%20for%20borrowers%20whose%20schools%20abruptly%20shut%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20education%20secretary%20would%20also%20be%20required%20to%20confirm%20that%20any%20new%20rules%20related%20to%20student-loan%20programs%20would%20not%20increase%20costs%20to%20the%20government%20%E2%80%94%20if%20they%20do%2C%20the%20rules%20cannot%20be%20implemented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20Democrats%20are%20proposing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20day%20before%20the%20markup%20on%20the%20GOP%20bill%2C%20House%20Democrats%20on%20the%20education%20committee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdemocrats-edworkforce.house.gov%2Fissues%2Froadmap-to-college-student-success%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintroduced%3C%2Fa%3E%20their%20plan%20to%20address%20college%20affordability%3A%20the%20Roadmap%20to%20College%20Student%20Success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20consists%20of%20a%20package%20of%20Democratic-led%20legislation%20that%20addresses%2