0State%20Cricket%20Association%20(KCA)%20Ranji%20team%20manager%20Ramesh%20told%20ANI%20that%20the%20Karnataka%20skipper's%20statement%20is%20being%20recorded%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMayank%20Agarwal%20is%20out%20of%20danger%20now%20and%20his%20statement%20is%20being%20recorded%20by%20the%20police...we%20don't%20know%20in%20detail%20on%20this%20matter%2C%20we%20are%20taking%20him%20to%20Bengaluru%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETripura%20Cricket%20Association%20(TCA)%20working%20secretary%20Basudeb%20Chakraborty%20had%20said%20earlier%20that%20during%20the%20flight%20Mayank%20drank%20from%20a%20bottle%20which%20led%20to%20his%20feeling%20sick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20sent%20TCA%20staff%20to%20the%20hospital%20and%20they%20conveyed%20that%20there%20was%20a%20bottle%2C%20Mayank%20drank%20it%20assuming%20that%20it%20was%20water%20and%20after%20drinking%20it%20he%20felt%20acidic%20and%20it%20gave%20a%20burning%20sensation%2C%26quot%3B%20Basudeb%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flight%20to%20Delhi%20returned%20to%20Agartala%20due%20to%20a%20medical%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ESPNcricinfo%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20team%20manager%2C%20on%20behalf%20of%20Agarwal%2C%20has%20also%20requested%20the%20Tripura%20police%20to%20investigate%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20written%20complaint%20has%20been%20given%20to%20K%20Kiran%20Kumar%2C%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(Tripura%20West)%20and%20a%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20New%20Capital%20Complex%20Police%20Station%20in%20Agartala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMayank%20has%20been%20a%20crucial%20figure%20for%20Karnataka%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20this%20season.%20In%20the%20ongoing%20Ranji%20Trophy%2C%20he%20has%20struck%20two%20hundreds%20and%20a%20half-century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20are%20currently%20second%20in%20Group%20C%20with%20two%20wins%2C%20a%20draw%20and%20a%20defeat%20i