%2F02%2Fvladimir-putin-net-worth-2022%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFortune%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20all%20this%2C%20the%20famous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fnews%2F2016%2Fapr%2F03%2Fpanama-papers-money-hidden-offshore%5C%22%3EPanama%20Papers%3C%2Fa%3E%20revealed%20a%20network%20of%20secret%20offshore%20deals%20and%20loans%20worth%20%242%20billion%20pointing%20to%20Mr%20Putin%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Putin%20has%20denied%20all%20these%20allegations%2C%20but%20admitted%20to%20different%20form%20of%20riches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20the%20wealthiest%20man%2C%20not%20just%20in%20Europe%20but%20in%20the%20whole%20world%3A%20I%20collect%20emotions.%20I%20am%20wealthy%20in%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Russia%20have%20twice%20entrusted%20me%20with%20the%20leadership%20of%20a%20great%20nation%20such%20as%20Russia.%20I%20believe%20that%20is%20my%20greatest%20wealth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reporter%20Steven%20Lee%20Myers%20in%20his%20book%20'%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Tsar%3C%2Fem%3E'.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706693340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F3qjg5pu_elon-musk-putin_625x300_28_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fis-vladimir-putin-richer-than-elon-musk-read-what-tesla-ceo-said-4966307%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Officially%2C%20Elon%20Musk's%20net%20worth%20is%20%24204.7%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20Forbes%20data.%20Though%20he%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20six%20companies%2C%20reports%20say%20Vladimir%20Putin%20owns%2020%20houses%2C%20700%20cars%2C%2058%20aircraft%20and%20helicopters%2C%20and%20a%20%24716%20million%20plane.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fis-vladimir-putin-richer-than-elon-musk-read-what-tesla-ceo-said-4966307%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fis-vladimir-putin-richer-than-elon-musk-read-what-tesla-ceo-said-4966307%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fis-vladimir-putin-richer-than-elon-musk-read-what-tesla-ceo-said-4966307%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BKindly%20Move%20Out%26quot%3B%3A%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%2C%20Daughter%20Told%20After%20Ram%20Temple%20Post%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%20and%20his%20daughter%20Suranya%20Aiyar%20have%20received%20a%20notice%20to%20vacate%20their%20home%20in%20Delhi's%20Jangpura%20over%20a%20social%20media%20post%20condemning%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Temple%20consecration%20ceremony%20on%20January%2022.%20The%20notice%2C%20sent%20by%20the%20Resident's%20Welfare%20Association%20(RWA)%20urges%20them%20to%20not%20indulge%20in%20rants%20which%20may%20disturb%20peace%20of%20hurt%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20other%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20appreciate%20a%20resident%20rant%20which%20may%20disturb%20the%20peace%20in%20the%20colony%20or%20hurt%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20the%20residents%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notice%20read.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20case%20you%20think%20what%20you%20have%20done%20in%20protesting%20against%20the%20consecration%20of%20Ram%20mandir%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20we%20would%20suggest%20you%20to%20kindly%20move%20out%20to%20another%20colony%20where%20people%20can%20turn%20blind%20eye%20to%20such%20hatred%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuranya%20Aiyar%2C%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%20on%20January%2020%2C%20had%20claimed%20that%20she%20is%20fasting%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20'Pran%20Pratishtha'%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir.%20She%20said%20that%20the%20fast%20was%20an%20expression%20of%20love%20and%20sorrow%20to%20fellow%20Muslim%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20response%2C%20RWA%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20Ms%20Aiyar%20said%20through%20social%20media%20was%20unbecoming%20of%20an%20educated%20person%2C%20who%20should%20have%20understood%20that%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20was%20being%20built%20after%20500%20years%20and%20that%20too%20after%205-0%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20might%20take%20the%20cover%20of%20freedom%20of%20speech%20but%20please%20remember%20as%20per%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20freedom%20of%20speech%20cannot%20be%20absolute%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Aiyar%20has%20been%20urged%20to%20condemn%20his%20daughter's%20post%20or%20leave%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20association%20urged%20the%20Aiyars%20to%20not%20provoke%20people%20and%20create%20hatred%20and%20mistrust%20among%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20may%20do%20whatever%20in%20politics%20for%20the%20good%20of%20your%20country%2C%20but%20please%20remember%20whatever%20you%20say%20and%20your%20actions%20count%20thus%20bringing%20good%20or%20bad%20name%20to%20the%20colony.%20Therefore%2C%20you%20are%20requested%20to%20please%20refrain%20from%20making%20such%20posts%2Fcomments%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20was%20a%20grand%20affair%2C%20celebrated%20by%20millions%20of%20Hindus%20not%20just%20in%20India%2C%20but%20across%20the%20globe.%20The%20temple%20has%20been%20built%20on%20a%202.67-acre%20site%20inside%20a%2070-acre%20complex%20and%20only%20its%20first%20phase%20is%20ready.%20The%20second%20and%20final%20phase%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20December%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20is%20estimated%20to%20cost%20Rs%201%2C500%20crores%20and%20is%20entirely%20funded%20by%20donations%20from%20within%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20opening%20on%20January%2022%2C%20thousands%20of%20Hindus%20have%20braved%20biting%20cold%20to%20pray%20at%20the%20new%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706693340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fr5m6h6ls_mani-shankar-aiyar-ani_625x300_31_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkindly-move-out-notice-to-congress-mani-shankar-aiyar-daughter-for-post-on-ram-temple-4965891%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%20and%20his%20daughter%20Suranya%20Aiyar%20have%20received%20a%20notice%20to%20vacate%20their%20home%20in%20Delhi's%20Jangpura%20over%20a%20social%20media%20post%20condemning%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Temple%20consecration%20ceremony%20on%20January%2022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkindly-move-out-notice-to-congress-mani-shankar-aiyar-daughter-for-post-on-ram-temple-4965891%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkindly-move-out-notice-to-congress-mani-shankar-aiyar-daughter-for-post-on-ram-temple-4965891%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkindly-move-out-notice-to-congress-mani-shankar-aiyar-daughter-for-post-on-ram-temple-4965891%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hindustan%20Coca-Cola%20Beverages%20achieves%20carbon%20neutrality%20at%20K'taka%20plant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706693213000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F30%2Ffull%2F1701349945-6075.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhindustan-coca-cola-beverages-achieves-carbon-neutrality-at-k-taka-plant-124013100421_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20prestigious%20certification%20by%20DNV%2C%20the%20globally%20accredited%20registrar%20and%20classification%20society%2C%20will%20be%20issued%20to%20Hindustan%20Coca-Cola%20Beverage%20Pvt%20Ltd%20(HCCB)%20in%20May%202024%22%