%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Patna%3A%20When%20asked%20%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20is%20taking%20credit%20for%20the%20caste%20census%20in%20Bihar%26quot%3B%2C%20Bihar%20CM%20Nitish%20Kumar%20says%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20Has%20he%20forgotten%20when%20the%20caste%20census%20happened%3F%20I%20conducted%20it%20in%20the%20presence%20of%209%20parties.%20In%202019-2020%2C%20I%20would%20talk%20about%20conducting%20caste%20census...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTZJ9XZ5SqO%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FTZJ9XZ5SqO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn-%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1752587823046369738%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2031%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsse%20badhkar%20koi%20faltu%20cheez%20hai%3F%20(Can%20there%20be%20a%20more%20nonsensical%20claim%3F)%20Has%20he%20forgotten%20when%20the%20caste%20census%20happened%3F%20I%20conducted%20it%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20nine%20parties.%20In%202019-2020%2C%20I%20would%20talk%20about%20caste%20census%20everywhere%2C%20from%20assembly%20to%20public%20meetings.%20I%20also%20met%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20I%20did%20it.%20They%20(Congress)%20were%20on%20the%20other%20side%20then.%20If%20someone%20tries%20to%20take%20false%20credit...%20Let%20it%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kumar%20told%20the%20media%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20days%20after%20he%20parted%20ways%20with%20the%20RJD%20and%20Congress%20and%20rejoined%20the%20NDA%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20claimed%20that%20Mr%20Kumar%20wriggled%20out%20of%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20because%20he%20felt%20%26quot%3Btrapped%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20caste%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20understand%20that%20Nitish%20Kumar%20was%20feeling%20trapped%20after%20the%20Congress%20and%20RJD%20ensured%20that%20a%20caste%20survey%20was%20held.%20The%20BJP%20provided%20him%20with%20a%20way%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Bihar's%20Purnea.%20The%20Congress%20MP%20is%20now%20in%20Bihar%20for%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20Congress's%20last-ditch%20attempt%20to%20rally%20support%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20doubled%20down%20on%20his%20earlier%20charge%20that%20there%20was%20no%20forward%20movement%20within%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20for%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20trying%20so%20hard.%20They%20did%20not%20do%20even%20one%20thing.%20Till%20today%2C%20they%20haven't%20decided%20which%20party%20will%20contest%20how%20many%20seats.%20This%20is%20why%20I%20left%20them%20and%20came%20back%20to%20who%20I%20was%20with%20initially.%20I%20will%20keep%20working%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Bihar%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Kumar%2C%20who%20was%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20bringing%20Opposition%20parties%20under%20one%20umbrella%20to%20take%20on%20the%20formidable%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar's%20party%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20United%2C%20has%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20trying%20to%20hijack%20the%20Opposition%20bloc.%20Soon%20after%20Mr%20Kumar's%20switch%2C%20senior%20JDU%20leader%20KC%20Tyagi%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20disrupting%20the%20seat-sharing%20process%20and%20making%20disproportionate%20demands%20on%20allies.%20%26quot%3BCongress%20kept%20dragging%20the%20seat%20sharing%2C%20we%20kept%20saying%20that%20seat%20sharing%20needs%20to%20happen%20immediately.%20INDIA%20lacked%20plans%20to%20fight%20against%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tyagi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20also%20hit%20back%20at%20his%20former%20deputy%20and%20RJD%20leader%20Tejashwi%20Yadav's%20remarks%20on%20the%20work%20done%20by%20the%20JDU-RJD%20government%20after%20it%20took%20over%20in%202022%20--%20after%20Mr%20Kumar's%20last%20flip-flop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CM%20who%20used%20to%20say%20that%20it%20is%20impossible%20to%20give%20jobs%2C%20we%20gave%20jobs%20and%20showed%20that%20it%20is%20possible.%20We%20brought%20new%20policies%20in%20tourism%2C%20IT%2C%20and%20sports.%20The%20work%20that%20was%20done%20in%2017%20months%20could%20not%20be%20done%20in%2017%20years%20(of%20BJP-JDU%20rule).%20We%20did%20historic%20work%20in%20the%2017%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20remarks%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20we%20forget%20the%20days%20before%202005%3F%26quot%3B%20He%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20corruption-%20and%20crime-tainted%20regime%20of%20RJD%20rule%20under%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706692680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F85q53olg_nitish-kumar-rahul-gandhi_625x300_25_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-jabs-rahul-gandhi-on-caste-count-i-did-it-he-claims-credit-4965565%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20sharp%20response%20to%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20on%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20today%20accused%20the%20Congress%20MP%20of%20trying%20to%20take%20credit%20for%20something%20he%20has%20not%20done.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-jabs-rahul-gandhi-on-caste-count-i-did-it-he-claims-credit-4965565%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-jabs-rahul-gandhi-on-caste-count-i-did-it-he-claims-credit-4965565%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnitish-kumar-jabs-rahul-gandhi-on-caste-count-i-did-it-he-claims-credit-4965565%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yemen's%20Huthis%20fire%20missiles%20at%20US%20warship%3A%20Rebel%20statement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706692505000%2C%22visual%22%3A%