20with%20the%20sale%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20highly-placed%20source%20in%20Washington%20told%20this%20reporter.%20The%20source%2C%20who%20operates%20at%20the%20top%20layer%20of%20US%20policymaking%2C%20cannot%20be%20identified%20as%20he%20is%20not%C2%A0%20authorised%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExplaining%20the%20delay%20in%20delivering%20these%20lethal%2C%20long-range%20weapons%20to%20India%2C%20the%20Washington-based%20source%20says%20that%20Indian-American%20lawmakers%20in%20particular%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20fallout%20from%20the%20indictment%20of%20an%20Indian%20named%20Nikhil%20Gupta.%20He%20has%20%C2%A0been%20formally%20charged%20with%20conspiring%20to%20kill%20Pannun%2C%20and%20is%20currently%20in%20detention%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20pending%20his%20deportation%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fpannun-murder-plot-significant-damage-likely-for-bilateral-ties-warn-indian-american-lawmakers%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20joint%20statement%20on%20the%20Pannun%20plot%20last%20December%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20five%20US%20Congress%20members%20of%20Indian%20origin%20%E2%80%93%20who%20received%20a%20classified%20briefing%20from%20the%20Biden%20administration%20on%20the%20federal%20indictment%20%E2%80%93%20said%20that%20it%20is%20critical%20for%20India%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfully%20investigate%20%5Band%5D%20hold%20those%20responsible%2C%20including%20Indian%20government%20officials%2C%20accountable%2C%20and%20provide%20assurances%20that%20this%20will%20not%20happen%20again%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUS%20federal%20prosecutors%20allege%20that%20Gupta%20had%20promised%20%24100%2C000%20to%20an%20FBI%20agent%20posing%20as%20a%20hitman%20to%20kill%20Pannun%20in%20New%20York.%20Gupta%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20on%20June%2030%20at%20America%E2%80%99s%20request.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20November%2029%2C%20US%20federal%20prosecutors%20charged%20Gupta%20with%20murder-for-hire%2C%20which%20carries%20up%20to%2010%20years%20in%20prison%3B%20and%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20murder-for-hire%2C%20which%20has%20a%20maximum%20sentence%20of%20a%2010-year%20jail%20term.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian-American%20lawmakers%20also%20warned%20of%20%E2%80%9Csignificant%20damage%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20US-India%20partnership%20if%20New%20Delhi%20does%20not%20address%20the%20situation%20directly%20and%20quickly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EContacted%20for%20comments%20on%20the%20delayed%20approvals%20for%20the%20drone%20deal%2C%20the%20US%20State%20Department%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20comment%20on%20arms%20sales%20until%20we%20have%20formally%20notified%20%5Bthe%20US%5D%20Congress%2C%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20Navy%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20defence%20ministry%20also%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20given%20its%20commitment%20to%20make%20a%20full%20accounting%20of%20the%20Pannun%20affair.%20And%20then%20the%20%5BCapitol%5D%20Hill%20is%20going%20to%20exercise%20its%20judgement%20on%20whether%20India%20has%20taken%20adequate%20measures%20or%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20Washington%20insider.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20played%20down%20the%20impact%20of%20this%20issue%20on%20Indo-US%20ties.%20In%20an%20interview%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Modi%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20strong%20bipartisan%20support%20for%20the%20strengthening%20of%20this%20relationship%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20think%20it%20appropriate%20%E2%80%9Cto%20link%20a%20few%20incidents%20with%20diplomatic%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Poseidon%20aircraft%20and%20Sea%20Guardian%20drones%20work%20together%2C%20watching%20over%20large%20swathes%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20and%20will%20give%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20an%20enhanced%20ability%20to%20respond%20to%20any%20attempts%20to%20disrupt%20international%20trade%20routes%20that%20pass%20through%20these%20waters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20versatile%20Sea%20Guardian%20drone%20has%20an%20endurance%20of%20over%2027%20hours%2C%20a%20speed%20of%20240%20knots%2C%20an%20operating%20ceiling%20of%2050%2C000%20feet%2C%20and%201%2C746%20kilograms%20of%20payload%20capacity%20that%20includes%201%2C361%20kilograms%20of%20external%20stores.%20The%20MQ-9A%20is%20powered%20by%20the%20Honeywell%20TPE331-10%20turboprop%20engine%2C%20which%20significantly%20improves%20engine%20performance%20and%20fuel%20efficiency%2C%20particularly%20at%20low%20altitudes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeing%20in%20operational%20service%20with%20the%20US%20military%2C%20the%20MQ-9A%20continues%20to%20evolve%2C%20keeping%20it%20relevant%20for%20its%20customers%E2%80%99%20emerging%20needs.%20The%20MQ-9A%20Extended%20Range%20(ER)%20was%20designed%20with%20field-retrofittable%20capabilities%20such%20as%20wing-borne%20fuel%20pods%20and%20a%20new%20reinforced%20landing%20gear%20that%20extends%20the%20aircraft%E2%80%99s%20already%20impressive%20endurance%20from%2027%20hours%20to%2034%20hours%2C%20while%20further%20increasing%20its%20operational%20flexibility%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706691336000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31142354%2FUntitled-design-1-5.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fus-drone-sale-sky-guardian-pannu-killing-investigation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Washington-based%20source%20says%20that%20Indian-American%20lawmakers%20in%20particular%20