0Penguin%20India%2C%20Oct%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20under%20review%20was%20written%20from%20the%20present%20standpoint%2C%20drawing%20a%20line%20between%20Modi%20and%20pre-Modi%20times.%20While%20refreshing%20our%20memories%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20collective%20national%20leadership%20from%20the%20national%20government%E2%80%99s%20early%20days%2C%20it%20ventilates%20how%20the%20constitutional%20bodies%20and%20positions%20have%20been%20compromised%20and%20demolished%20under%20the%20Prime%20Ministership%20of%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20aspects%20discussed%20in%20this%20book%20have%20been%20opined%20and%20debated%20in%20our%20everyday%20public%20discourse.%20Still%2C%20the%20book%20stitched%20them%20more%20systematically%20to%20unfold%20the%20damage%20being%20done%20to%20the%20country%20in%20the%20last%20decade%20and%20the%20danger%20if%20Modi%20beats%20the%20hat-trick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%E2%80%99s%20editors%20have%20explained%20these%20things%20much%20more%20lucidly%20in%20their%20lengthy%20Introduction%20chapter%20and%20the%20epilogue.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Introduction%E2%80%99%20chapter%20sets%20the%20tone%20for%20the%20book%20by%20discussing%20how%20India%20as%20a%20state%20and%20a%20nation%20has%20been%20carved%20and%20maintained%20carefully%2C%20accommodating%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20diversities%20by%20our%20first-generation%20national%20leaders%20from%20the%20days%20of%20the%20national%20movement.%20The%20epilogue%20emphasises%20the%20need%20to%20recover%20the%20lost%20liberal%2C%20secular%2C%20and%20democratic%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDecline%20in%20institutional%20freedom%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98First%20Chapter%E2%80%99%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20discusses%20how%20the%20Congress%20Party%20strived%20to%20deepen%20these%20modern%20ideas%20of%20human%20freedom%20and%20weave%20multiple%20voices%20into%20a%20national%20symphony.%20Gandhi%20shares%20her%20experiences%20working%20twice%20in%20the%20National%20Advisory%20Council%20(NAC)%20during%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government.%20She%20underlines%20how%20the%20NAC%20as%20a%20collective%20leadership%20was%20crucial%20to%20accommodating%20multiple%20voices%20and%20diversities%20of%20India%20in%20the%20decision-making%20and%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collective%20leadership%20involving%20the%20civil%20society%20bodies%20and%20stakeholders%20had%20passed%20the%20most%20revolutionary%20Acts%20during%20the%20two%20UPA%20governments%2C%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%2C%20Right%20to%20Employment%20(MGNREGA)%20Act%2C%20Forest%20Right%20Act%2C%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%2C%20Right%20to%20Education%20Act.%20These%20acts%20brought%20about%20a%20paradigm%20shift%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20its%20citizens%2C%20a%20shift%20from%20welfarism%20to%20the%20right%20approach%20that%20resulted%20in%20a%20tangible%20change%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20oppressed%20and%20marginalised%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Modi%20regime%2C%20all%20these%20mechanisms%20of%20collective%20leadership%20have%20been%20wrecked%2C%20and%20only%20a%20singular%20leadership%20is%20established%2C%20which%20is%20detrimental%20to%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20(PMO)%2C%20consisting%20of%20a%20few%20civil%20servants%2C%20has%20become%20the%20sole%20decision-making%20body%20while%20reducing%20the%20ministers%20to%20mere%20rubber%20stamps.%20And%20the%20only%20guiding%20body%20to%20the%20government%20is%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20the%20parent%20organisation%20of%20the%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party.%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBoth%20these%20developments%20make%20a%20mockery%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20parliamentary%20democracy%2C%20while%20the%20former%20undermines%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20the%20state%20itself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remaining%20chapter%20delineates%20in%20a%20nuanced%20way%20how%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20has%20vilified%20the%20constitutional%20bodies%20and%20ethos%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%20While%20discussing%20the%20various%20trajectories%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20our%20parliament%2C%20Hamid%20Ansari%20says%20parliament%20is%20diminished%20from%20its%20primary%20duty%20of%20controlling%20the%20political%20executive%20under%20the%20present%20regime.%20India%20is%20now%20reduced%20to%20a%20symbolic%20democracy%2C%20no%20longer%20a%20vibrant%20parliamentary%20democracy%2C%20but%20rather%20becoming%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20illiberal%20democracy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYechury%E2%80%99s%20essay%20is%20interesting%20in%20many%20respects%2C%20as%20it%20explores%20the%20tradition%20of%20coalition%20culture%20and%20politics%20embedded%20in%20Indian%20soil%20from%20early%20historical%20times.%20He%20says%20the%20coalition%20politics%20of%20post-independent%20India%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20coalition%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20diversity%2C%20which%20was%20designed%20to%20defend%20the%20Indian%20constitution%2C%20to%20safeguard%20the%20guarantees%2C%20freedom%2C%20and%20fundamental%20rights%20ensured%20to%20citizens%2C%20and%20to%20defend%20the%20economic%20sovereignty%20of%20our%20country%20and%20the%20constitutional%20%E2%80%98idea%20of%20India%E2%80%99.%20It%20is%20on%20these%20principles%20and%20spirit%20that%20the%20INDIA%20coalition%20is%20formed%20to%20put%20a%20check%20on%20the%20RSS-BJP%20vision%20of%20India%20that%20aims%20to%20destroy%20the%20unity%2C%20integrity%2C%20and%20diversity%20of%20our%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAttack%20on%20institutional%20freedom%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chapter%20on%20judiciary%20appraises%20the%20tension%20between%20the%20political%20executive%20and%20the%20judiciary%20but%20makes%20a%20sharp%20comment%20on%20the%20appointment%20practices%20of%20judges%20of%20higher%20courts%20by%20saying%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20problem%20is%20not%20how%20appointments%20are%20made%20but%20who%20is%20appointed%20and%20who%20is%20disappointed.%20Indian%20judiciary%20is%20dwindling%20to%20maintain%20its%20core%20principles%20%E2%80%93%20independence%2C%20impartiality%2C%20integrity%2C%20property%2C%20equality%2C%20competence%2C%20and%20diligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20the%20role%20of%20the%20governor%20is%20the%20most%20controversial%20in%20the%20Indian%20political%20system.%20Alva%20shows%20examples%20of%20how%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Union%20government%20has%20insidiously%20misused%20state%20governors%20to%20engineer%20the%20collapse%2Fdismissal%20of%20the%20elected%20government%20and%20interfere%20in%20the%20governance%20of%20states.%20She%20says%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20unleashed%20havoc%2C%20not%20just%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%20but%20also%20on%20the%20nation%2C%20and%20the%20governors%20are%20not%20now%20constitutional%20statesmen%20but%20unconstitutional%20hitmen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F15125309%2FNirvachan-Sadan-TW-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668180%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20building%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40PIB_INDIA.%20November%205%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20is%20another%20constitutional%20body%20that%20received%20bitter%20criticism%20for%20failing%20to%20prevent%20electoral%20fraud%20and%20crimes.%20The%20relationship%20between%20the%20Election%20Commission%20and%20the%20ruling%20party%20is%20always%20questioned%20despite%20the%20mechanism%20that%20evolved%20to%20check%20such%20misuses%20of%20the%20EC.%20Lavasa%20shows%20how%20the%20eminence%20of%20EC%20has%20been%20diluted%20during%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20regime%3B%20rather%2C%20it%20became%20reactive%20in%20many%20cases.%20Despite%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%20the%20EC%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20the%20vandalism%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%20during%20the%20election.%20In%20one%20case%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20termed%20the%20EC%20%E2%80%98toothless%E2%80%99.%20In%20any%20parliamentary%20democratic%20system%2C%20the%20EC%E2%80%99s%20role%20is%20crucial.%20In%20fact%2C%20democracy%20is%20judged%20based%20on%20the%20electoral%20process.%20India%20has%20been%20classified%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98flawed%20democracy%E2%80%99%20as%20per%20the%20global%20democracy%20index%20of%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%E2%80%99s%20federal%20system%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20on%20the%20spirit%20of%20unity%20in%20diversity%2C%20has%20equally%20been%20subjected%20to%20the%20onslaught%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%20The%20founder%20of%20India%20tilted%20towards%20a%20strong%20Union%20government%20because%20of%20the%20partition%20and%20cession%20movements%20following%20the%20independence.%20However%2C%20care%20was%20taken%20to%20balance%20Centre-state%20relations%20through%20various%20mechanisms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20essay%2C%20Isaac%20examines%20how%20these%20mechanisms%20failed%20over%20time%2C%20particularly%20the%20Union%20Finance%20Commission%2C%20Planning%20Commission%2C%20National%20Development%20Council%2C%20Goods%20and%20Service%20Tax%20(GST)%20Council%2C%20and%20NITI%20Aayog.%20The%20latter%20two%20were%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20inventions.%20Planning%20Commission%20was%20an%20important%20check%20on%20the%20Union%20finance%20ministry.%20But%20it%20was%20replaced%20with%20NITI%20Aayog%2C%20which%20is%20an%20advisory%20body.%20Importantly%2C%20it%20is%20neither%20a%20constitutional%20nor%20a%20statutory%20body.%20GST%20is%20indeed%20a%20big%20blow%20to%20the%20states.%20With%20this%2C%20the%20state%20governments%20lost%20their%20power%20to%20tax%20their%20state%20people.%20Isaac%20shows%20how%20GST%20has%20become%20a%20continuous%20contestation%20between%20the%20Union%20and%20State%20governments%2C%20particularly%20where%20opposition%20is%20ruling%20the%20state.%20He%20says%20the%20overall%20trend%20presently%20has%20been%20towards%20greater%20centralisation%20and%20weakening%20of%20the%20states%2C%20which%20seriously%20affects%20India%E2%80%99s%20federal%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHabibullah%E2%80%99s%20essay%20on%20the%20Information%20Commissions%20of%20India%20unfolds%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20government%20subverted%20the%20RTI%20Act%2C%20which%20the%20UPA%20government%20designed%20to%20bring%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20in%20governance.%20During%20the%202014%20election%20campaign%2C%20Modi%20sloganed%20maximum%20governance%20with%20minimum%20government%2C%20good%20governance%2C%20sabka%20saath%2C%20and%20sabka%20vikas%2C%20but%20he%20took%20a%20completely%20opposite%20position%20once%20he%20came%20into%20power.%20The%20RTI%20Act%2C%20which%20is%20instrumental%20in%20strengthening%20democracy%2C%20has%20been%20subverted%20by%20rejecting%20requests%20for%20information%20under%20the%20Act%2C%20not%20appointing%20commissioners%20of%20the%20Information%20Commission%2C%20and%20diluting%20the%20true%20spirit%20of%20the%20Act%20by%20amending%20it.%20In%20many%20cases%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20misused%20the%20Act%20to%20evade%20answerability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chapter%20on%20Indian%20bureaucracy%20by%20Saxena%20discusses%20the%20misuse%20of%20power%20in%20detail%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%20While%20narrating%20various%20functional%20problems%20of%20the%20Indian%20bureaucracy%2C%20Saxena%20says%20that%20India%20could%20not%20achieve%20economic%20development%20owing%20to%20the%20nexus%20between%20civil%20servants%20and%20politicians%20in%20looting%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20resources.%20He%20attributes%20the%20civil%20servants%20to%20the%20underdevelopment%20of%20India.%20Recently%2C%20NITI%20Aayog%20claimed%20that%2024.8%20crore%20Indians%20were%20lifted%20out%20of%20poverty%20in%20the%20nine%20years%20of%20the%20two%20NDA%20regimes%2C%20but%20India%20ranked%2094%20among%20107%20countries%20in%20the%20Global%20Hunger%20Index%202020.%20The%20Modi%20government%20has%20aggressively%20promoted%20patronaged%20administrative%20culture%2C%20often%20placing%20Gujarat%20and%20RSS%20ideology-inclined%20civil%20servants%20in%20higher%20important%20positions.%20Unlike%20earlier%20governments%2C%20the%20PMO%20has%20become%20the%20supreme%20authority%20in%20making%20all%20the%20decisions%20of%20the%20ministries.%20Ministers%20are%20just%20symbolic.%20The%20lack%20of%20collective%20leadership%20severely%20affects%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20administration%20and%20economic%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20chapter%20by%20Srinath%20deals%20with%20civil%20society%20in%20India.%20Civil%20society%20is%20crucial%20in%20any%20given%20society%20to%20defend%20democracy%2C%20freedom%2C%20and%20civic%20rights.%20Srinath%20gives%20an%20illuminating%20account%20of%20the%20challenges%20civil%20society%20bodies%20face%2C%20citing%20evidence%20from%20government%20reports.%20Particularly%2C%20the%20changes%20brought%20in%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20check%20the%20activities%20of%20civil%20society%2C%20including%20financial%20transactions%2C%20have%20created%20a%20hostile%20atmosphere%20in%20the%20country.%20Activists%2C%20journalists%2C%20academicians%2C%20cartoonists%2C%20and%20even%20students%20have%20been%20targeted%20by%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20for%20raising%20their%20voices%20against%20divisive%20and%20unjust%20policies%20of%20the%20government.%20Being%20critical%20of%20the%20government%20policies%20is%20seen%20as%20%E2%80%98anti-national%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Modi%20regime%2C%20the%20regime%20unchallenged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20essentially%20highlights%20the%20lack%20of%20collective%20leadership%20in%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20which%20has%20been%20endeavoring%20to%20undermine%20the%20constitutional%20bodies%20and%20institutions.%20It%20shows%20how%20the%20Constitution%20is%20under%20threat.%20Even%20in%20the%20pre-Modi%20BJP%20regimes%2C%20there%20used%20to%20be%20dozens%20of%20credible%20national%20leaders%20in%20BJP%20government.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20personification%20has%20killed%20all%20the%20credible%20leaders%20in%20the%20BJP.%20The%20individual%20cult%20leadership%20is%20not%20only%20dangerous%20to%20any%20political%20party%20but%20also%20to%20the%20country.%20The%20book%2C%20indeed%2C%20unfolds%20the%20damage%20done%20to%20the%20Indian%20nation%20under%20the%20dictatorial%20leadership%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20argues%20for%20collective%20leadership.%20It%20is%20a%20must-read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBhangya%20Bhukya%20is%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20History%2C%20University%20of%20Hyderabad%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706689846000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F06124906%2FUntitled-design-8.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fthe-collapse-of-collective-leadership-under-narendra-modi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2