%20This%20amount%20also%20includes%20income%20from%20bank%20deposits%2C%20a%20military%20pension%20and%20money%20he%20made%20from%20property%20sales.%20He%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fputin-formally-registered-as-presidential-candidate-for-march-polls-4953684%5C%22%3Efighting%20the%20presidential%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20in%20March%2C%20and%20will%20most%20certainly%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Putin%20has%20been%20in%20power%20for%20several%20decades%20-%20as%20Russia's%20president%20from%202000%20to%202008%20and%20since%202012%2C%20with%20a%20stint%20as%20Prime%20Minister.%20The%20official%20figures%20about%20his%20income%20were%20released%20after%20he%20formally%20filed%20nomination%20for%20the%20March%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20contrast%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States%20has%20an%20annual%20salary%20of%20%24400%2C000%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fputin-claims-hes-made-less-1-million-president-past-6-years-1865417%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENewsweek%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia's%20Central%20Election%20Commission%20(CEC)%20said%20that%20Mr%20Putin%20has%20savings%20of%2054.5%20million%20rubles%20(%24606%2C000)%20in%2010%20different%20bank%20accounts%20and%20he%20also%20owns%20a%20few%20vehicles.%20These%20are%3A%20two%20vintage%20Soviet%20Unions%20cars%20-%20GAZ%20M-21s%20-%20manufactured%20in%20the%201960s%2C%20a%20Russian-made%204X4%20from%202009%20and%20a%201987%20camping%20trailer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20president%20also%20owns%20an%20apartment%20in%20Moscow%2C%20and%20an%20apartment%20and%20a%20garage%20in%20St%20Petersburg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20documents%20were%20released%20a%20day%20after%20a%20%3Cem%3EMoscow%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20claimed%20he%20has%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvideo-claims-to-show-vladimir-putins-secret-residence-near-finland-4957606%5