C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F04192003%2Fstatecraft.png%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-237577%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22233%5C%22%3EThis%20was%20the%20classic%20old%20India.%20The%20two%20principal%20practitioners%20of%20old%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20and%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%20%E2%80%93%20found%20Nitish%20to%20be%20the%20sort%20of%20political%20operative%20with%20whom%20they%20could%20do%20business%20in%20a%20mutually%20beneficial%20way.%20In%20Bihar%2C%20an%20association%20with%20Nitish%20brought%20the%20BJP%20some%20much-needed%20respectability%3B%20in%20Delhi%2C%20a%20cabinet%20berth%20in%20the%20Vajpayee%20government%20garnered%20for%20Nitish%20the%20reputation%20of%20being%20an%20%E2%80%9Cadministrator%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Hindutva%20establishment%20needed%20a%20beach-head%20in%20Lalu%E2%80%99s%20Bihar%2C%20and%20Nitish%20was%20there%20to%20help%20them%20undertake%20the%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20it%20must%20be%20said%20to%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20credit%20that%20he%20never%20changed%20his%20spots.%20He%20remains%20a%20practitioner%20par%20excellence%20of%20old%20politics%20of%20old%20India.%20He%20refused%20to%20understand%20the%20Hindutva%20crowd%E2%80%99s%20long%20term%20political%20intentions%3B%20he%20was%20perfectly%20at%20ease%20in%20communal%20company%20%E2%80%93%20just%20like%20a%20H.D.%20Kumaraswamy%20%E2%80%93%20as%20long%20he%20could%20stay%20in%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20bungalow.%20He%20turned%20a%20Nelson%E2%80%99s%20eye%20as%20the%20Hindutva%20crowd%20flooded%20the%20moat%20around%20his%20increasingly%20fragile%20fort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20if%20this%20very%20Nitish%20is%2C%20once%20again%2C%20being%20welcomed%20by%20the%20strident%20chief%20priests%20of%20New%20India%2FNaya%20Bharat%20%E2%80%93%20that%20too%20within%20days%20of%20that%20mind-numbing%20saturation%20coverage%20of%20a%20certain%20event%20in%20Ayodhya%20%E2%80%93%20then%20it%20simply%20means%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strategists%20know%20that%20the%20presumed%20%E2%80%9CRam%20wave%E2%80%9D%20is%20going%20to%20peter%20out%20soon.%20In%20fact%2C%20these%20neo-Chanakyas%20had%20already%20betrayed%20their%20nervousness%20when%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkarpoori-thakur-bharat-ratna%5C%22%3Eannounced%20for%20Karpoori%20Thakur%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%20%7C%20Has%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Brought%20into%20Focus%20the%20Sad%20and%20Sorry%20Truth%20of%20Indian%20Politics%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvideo-karan-thapar-kapil-sibal-nitish-kumar-amit-shah%5C%22%3EHas%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Brought%20into%20Focus%20the%20Sad%20and%20Sorry%20Truth%20of%20Indian%20Politics%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20when%20the%20country%20was%20being%20told%20that%20a%20new%20era%20of%20nobility%20and%20virtuousness%20had%20dawned%2C%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar%20caper%20has%20jolted%20us%20back%20to%20the%20reality%20that%20nothing%20has%20changed.%20If%20the%20new%20age%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20has%20been%20inaugurated%2C%20why%20was%20this%20personification%20of%20old%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20of%20opportunism%20and%20expediency%20%E2%80%93%20so%20warmly%20welcomed%20by%20those%20very%20%E2%80%9Csevaks%E2%80%9D%20who%20wear%20righteousness%20on%20their%20saffron%20sleeves%3F%20Which%20ever%20way%20you%20slice%20him%2C%20Nitish%20is%20the%20very%20antithesis%20of%20each%20and%20every%20tenet%20of%20Ram%20Rajya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20should%20be%20grateful%20to%20Nitish%20for%20showing%20up%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20such%20unfavourable%20light.%20Here%20was%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20observing%20a%20diet%20protocol%2C%20temple-hopping%20for%20days%2C%20going%20through%20all%20those%20rituals%20on%20January%2022%20at%20Ayodhya%2C%20trying%20to%20carve%20out%20for%20himself%20the%20persona%20of%20a%20quasi-saint.%20The%20country%20was%20appropriately%20impressed.%20And%20now%2C%20the%20same%20sections%20of%20Hindu%20society%20can%20see%20for%20themselves%20how%20an%20old%20sinner%20steeped%20in%20political%20dishonesty%20and%20chicanery%20has%20been%20embraced%20as%20a%20valuable%20asset.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20has%20not%20only%20brought%20himself%20down%20in%20public%20esteem%2C%20he%20has%20pulled%20Modi%20down%20more%20than%20a%20peg%20too.%20What%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20exertions%20on%20his%20arduous%20yatras%20could%20not%20achieve%2C%20Nitish%20has%20accomplished%20in%20a%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20may%20be%20able%20to%20help%20the%20BJP%20hold%20on%20to%20its%20current%20Lok%20Sabha%20tally%20in%20Bihar%2C%20yet%20his%20return%20to%20the%20NDA%20fold%20will%20not%20enhance%20the%20efficacy%20of%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20political%20narrative.%20After%20all%2C%20voters%20throughout%20the%20country%20have%20heard%20all%20the%20bad%20names%20that%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20leaders%2C%20spokespersons%20and%20embedded%20journalists%20and%20anchors%20have%20heaped%20on%20Nitish%20in%20recent%20months.%20Now%20it%20will%20require%20extraordinary%20linguistic%20and%20rhetorical%20contortions%20for%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20explain%20and%20justify%20the%20return%20of%20such%20a%20magnificently%20abused%20politico%20to%20the%20noble%20company%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Amit%20Shah.%20Voters%20will%20be%20left%20deciding%20for%20themselves%20whether%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20speaking%20the%20truth%20now%20when%20they%20praise%20Nitish%20or%20whether%20they%20were%20telling%20lies%20when%20they%20were%20castigating%20him%20for%20keeping%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20company%2C%20or%20vice-versa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22This%20Election%20Season%2C%20Who%20Gets%20to%20Take%20the%20Credit%20for%20Jobs%20and%20Reservation%20in%20Bihar%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthis-election-season-who-gets-to-take-the-credit-for-jobs-and-reservation-in-bihar%5C%22%3EThis%20Election%20Season%2C%20Who%20Gets%20to%20Take%20the%20Credit%20for%20Jobs%20and%20Reservation%20in%20Bihar%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20parties%2C%20especially%20those%20in%20Bihar%2C%20should%20be%20able%20to%20creatively%20use%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20about-turn%20to%20defuse%20and%20blunt%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20anti-corruption%20rhetoric.%20If%20the%20RJD%20and%20its%20leadership%20are%20to%20be%20maligned%20as%20%E2%80%9Ccorrupt%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fpatna%2Fnitish-lalu-alliance-is-taking-bihar-back-to-jungle-raj-amit-shah%2Farticleshow%2F103723650.cms%5C%22%3Epractitioners%20of%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9Cjungle%20raj%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20then%20how%20come%20Nitish%20remained%20uncontaminated%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbad%E2%80%9D%20company%20he%20kept%20till%20recently%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbove%20all%2C%20the%20Nitish%20Kumar%20caper%20has%20forced%20every%20voter%20%E2%80%93%20except%20maybe%20the%20die-hard%20bhakts%20%E2%80%93%20to%20questions%20the%20pretensions%20and%20protestations%20of%20all%20our%20public%20leaders.%20Are%20we%20as%20a%20society%20comfortable%20with%20deceit%20and%20deception%20as%20the%20working%20mantra%20of%20our%20rulers%3F%20And%2C%20if%20these%20rulers%20are%20so%20untroubled%20by%20expediency%2C%20cynicism%20and%20moral%20indifference%2C%20then%20should%20their%20claims%20to%20have%20ushered%20in%20a%20new%20politics%20of%20selflessness%20and%20public%20service%20not%20be%20taken%20with%20more%20than%20a%20handful%20of%20salt%3F%20No%20society%20can%20achieve%20real%20greatness%20if%20its%20ruling%20clique%20remains%20shrouded%20in%20Machiavellian%20calculations%20and%20moral%20poverty.%20Nitish%20should%20be%20thanked%20for%20calling%20out%20the%20hoax%20that%20is%20Naya%20Bharat.%20The%20warm%20welcome%20he%