-global-500-2023-124013100312_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karnataka%20Governor%20Sends%20Ordinance%20on%2060%25%20Use%20of%20Kannada%20in%20Signboards%20Back%20to%20Govt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31115904%2FScreenshot-2024-01-31-at-11.58.51-AM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Karnataka%20governor%20Thaawarchand%20Gehlot%20has%20rejected%20an%20ordinance%20that%20attempts%20to%20increase%20the%20use%20of%20Kannada%20in%20signboards%20of%20businesses%20in%20the%20state%2C%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20D.K.%20Shivakumar%20revealed%20on%20Tuesday%20(January%2030).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20cabinet%20had%20approved%20the%20ordinance%20on%20January%205%20to%20amend%20the%20Kannada%20Language%20Comprehensive%20Development%20Act%20and%20mandate%2060%25%20use%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20language%20in%20signboards.%20Currently%2C%20the%20law%20requires%20the%20use%20of%20Kannada%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cupper-half%20portion%E2%80%9D%20of%20boards%20displaying%20the%20names%20of%20businesses%2C%20PTI%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fgovernor-rejects-ordinance-on-60-signage-in-kannada-2871822%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20made%20a%20law%20and%20approved%20an%20ordinance.%20The%20Governor%20could%20have%20given%20his%20assent.%20Instead%2C%20he%20has%20sent%20it%20back%20saying%20it%20should%20be%20passed%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shivakumar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fgovernor-rejects-ordinance-on-60-signage-in-kannada-2871822%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20without%20elaborating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20had%20approved%20the%20ordinance%20in%20wake%20of%20violent%20protests%20led%20by%20pro-Kannada%20groups%20targeting%20businesses%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20disagreement%20between%20the%20Siddaramaiah-led%20Congress%20government%20and%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20that%20has%20come%20out%20in%20the%20open%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20being%20speculated%20that%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20rejection%2C%20just%20ahead%20of%20the%20Budget%20session%20scheduled%20to%20begin%20next%20month%2C%20may%20have%20significance.%20Gehlot%20is%20set%20to%20address%20both%20houses%20of%20legislature%20on%20February%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddaramaiah%20had%20met%20Gehlot%20a%20day%20before%20Shivakumar%E2%80%99s%20announcement.%20According%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Gehlot%20signed%20off%20on%20three%20bills%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fgovernor-rejects-ordinance-on-60-signage-in-kannada-2871822%5C%22%3Ethe%20chief%20minister%20urged%20him%20to%20clear%20the%20bills%3C%2Fa%3E%20passed%20in%20the%20Belagavi%20session%20of%20the%20legislature%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20cleared%20bills%20eliminates%20compulsory%20rural%20service%20for%20medical%20graduates.%20However%2C%20of%20the%2017%20bills%20passed%20in%20the%20Belagavi%20session%2C%20the%20governor%20has%20assented%20to%20only%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20decision%20to%20scrap%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%20in%20Karnataka%20could%20strain%20relations%20between%20the%20state%20and%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan.%20Recently%2C%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Forum%20for%20Karnataka%20Education%20presented%20a%20petition%20signed%20by%2010%20lakh%20stakeholders%20to%20the%20governor%20seeking%20intervention%20to%20ensure%20the%20continuation%20of%20NEP%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706684409000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F31115904%2FScreenshot-2024-01-31-at-11.58.51-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fkarnataka-governor-sends-ordinance-on-6