0for%20Gaza%2C%20told%20correspondents%20at%20a%20stakeout%20outside%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fsecuritycouncil%2F%5C%22%3ESecurity%20Council%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Chamber%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20noted%20the%20key%20role%20the%20agency%20has%20played%20over%20decades%2C%20before%20the%20current%20conflict%2C%20in%20education%2C%20healthcare%20and%20other%20services.%20UNRWA%20was%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fundocs.org%2Fen%2FA%2FRES%2F302%2528IV%2529%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestablished%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%20the%20General%20Assembly%20in%20December%201949.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUNRWA%E2%80%99s%20operations%20are%20in%20jeopardy%20after%20several%20donor%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20United%20States%2C%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Germany%20and%20Japan%2C%20suspended%20funding%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20extremely%20serious%20allegations%20that%20several%20of%20its%20staff%20were%20involved%20in%20the%207%20October%20terror%20attacks%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Organization%20has%20initiated%20an%20investigation%2C%20and%20the%20Secretary-General%20has%20reiterated%20that%20any%20employee%20found%20to%20be%20involved%20will%20be%20held%20accountable%2C%20including%20through%20criminal%20prosecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%20appearance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaag%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20to%20the%20press%20followed%20her%20first%20closed-door%20briefing%20to%20the%20Security%20Council%20since%20taking%20up%20her%20key%20coordination%20role%20pursuant%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fundocs.org%2FS%2FRES%2F2720(2023)%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECouncil%20resolution%202720%20(2023)%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20mandate%20is%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2023%2F12%2F1145022%5C%22%3Efacilitate%2C%20coordinate%2C%20monitor%20and%20verify%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0humanitarian%20relief%20consignments%20to%20Gaza%20as%20well%20as%20establish%20a%20UN%20mechanism%20to%20accelerate%20humanitarian%20relief%20shipments%20to%20the%20enclave%20through%20States%20which%20are%20not%20party%20to%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaag%20underscored%20that%20the%20success%20of%20her%20mandate%20%E2%80%9Cis%20about%20the%20ability%20to%20achieve%20and%20meet%20the%20needs%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20civilians%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20is%20the%20only%20indicator%2C%20as%20far%20as%20I%20am%20concerned.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChallenges%20on%20the%20ground%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaag%20emphasised%20that%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%20is%20hampering%20aid%20efforts%20and%20causing%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20there%20is%20no%20space%2C%20given%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20is%20no%20ceasefire%20there%20and%20the%20conflict%20is%20raging.%C2%A0There%20is%20no%20space%20to%20have%20monitors%20all%20over%20Gaza%20to%20work%20with%20the%20agencies%20to%20see%2C%20to%20verify%20and%20monitor.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20reiterated%20the%20importance%20of%20increasing%20the%20flow%20of%20commercial%20goods%20into%20Gaza%20in%20addition%20to%20humanitarian%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCommercial%20goods%20need%20to%20be%20allowed%20back%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20will%20be%20no%20recovery%2C%20let%20alone%20reconstruction%20in%20future%2C%20without%20that%20broad%20bandwidth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeasoned%20humanitarian%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaag%2C%20of%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20has%20held%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20senior%20positions%20in%20the%20UN%20system.%20She%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fsg%2Fen%2Fcontent%2Fsg%2Fpersonnel-appointments%2F2023-12-26%2Fms-sigrid-kaag-of-the-netherlands-senior-humanitarian-and-reconstruction-coordinator-for-gaza-pursuant-security-council-resolution-2720-%25282023%2529%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappointed%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%20the%20Secretary-General%20on%2026%20December%202023%20and%20began%20her%20assignment%20on%208%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20Special%20Coordinator%20for%20Lebanon%20from%202015%20to%202017%20and%20from%202013%20to%202015%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Joint%20UN-Organization%20for%20Prohibition%20of%20Chemical%20Weapons%20Mission%20in%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20served%20as%20Assistant%20Secretary-General%20with%20the%20UN%20Development%20Programme%20(2010-13)%20and%20was%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unicef.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUNICEF%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Regional%20Director%20for%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20North%20Africa%20(2007-10).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20that%2C%20Kaag%20held%20several%20senior%20positions%20with%20the%20UN%20International%20Organization%20for%20Migration%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iom.int%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIOM%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20UNRWA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20speaks%20fluent%20Arabic%20and%20five%20other%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20held%20many%20senior%20roles%20in%20the%20Dutch%20Government%2C%20including%20as%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Foreign%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fabout-us%2Fcopyright%3F_gl%3D1*18772us*_ga*MTMzMjQ2NTE0Ni4xNjk3MTcwMTkx*_ga_TK9BQL5X7Z*MTcwNjY4MzA5Mi4yOS4wLjE3MDY2ODMwOTIuMC4wLjA.*_ga_S5EKZKSB78*MTcwNjY4MzA5Mi4yMi4wLjE3MDY2ODMwOTIuNjAuMC4w%5C%22%3EUN%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706683600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F