20raid%20against%20Soren%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fhemant-soren-delhi-house-ed-seize-cash-bmw-9134607%2F%5C%22%3Elaunch%20a%20shrill%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister.%20Immediately%20after%20the%20raids%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20when%20Soren%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20present%2C%20the%20BJP%20put%20up%20a%20%E2%80%98missing%20person%E2%80%99s%E2%80%99%20poster%20containing%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20picture%20and%20a%20reward%20of%20Rs%2011%2C000%20for%20the%20person%20who%20finds%20him%2C%20and%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20gone%20%E2%80%9Cmissing%E2%80%9D%2C%20in%20what%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20claim%20that%20Soren%20had%20been%20absconding.%20However%2C%20Soren%20emerged%20in%20the%20afternoon%20and%20attended%20a%20meeting%20with%20his%20party%20legislators.%20Soren%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20been%20preoccupied%20with%20prior%20scheduled%20official%20engagements%20and%20preparations%20for%20the%20state%20budget%2C%20and%20accused%20the%20ED%20of%20conducting%20raids%20out%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmalice%E2%80%9D%20and%20to%20further%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20agenda%E2%80%9D%20of%20disrupting%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20even%20RJD%20chief%20Lalu%20Prasad%2C%20who%20is%20severely%20ill%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fland-for-job-scam-case-rjd-chief-lalu-prasad-yadav-appears-before-ed-for-questioning%2Farticle67788200.ece%5C%22%3Ecalled%20for%20questioning%20by%20the%20ED%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20case%20that%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20had%20first%20registered%20in%20May%202022%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cland-for-jobs%E2%80%9D%20scam.%20The%20CBI%20has%20named%20Lalu%20Prasad%2C%20his%20wife%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Rabri%20Devi%2C%20and%20their%20son%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20and%20two%20daughters%20Misa%20Bharti%20and%20Hema%20Ya