s%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Feng%2Fxwfw_665399%2Fs2510_665401%2F202401%2Ft20240130_11236316.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EChinese%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Wang%20Wenbin%20said%20at%20a%20daily%20media%20briefing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20China%20%E2%80%9Cfirmly%20opposes%20double%20standards%20on%20counterterrorism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CChina%20stands%20for%20strengthening%20counterterrorism%20cooperation%20among%20all%20countries%20to%20jointly%20fight%20all%20forms%20of%20terrorism%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20the%20Chinese%20diplomat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECiting%20the%20allegations%20by%20Canada%20and%20US%20of%20the%20activities%20of%20Indian%20agents%20against%20separatists%20on%20their%20soil%2C%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20secretary%20claimed%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20network%20of%20extra-judicial%20and%20extra-territorial%20killings%20has%20become%20a%20global%20phenomenon%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20reaction%2C%20India%20claimed%20that%20it%20is%20Pakistan%20that%20is%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20epicentre%20of%20terrorism%2C%20organised%20crime%2C%20and%20illegal%20transnational%20activities%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20and%20many%20other%20countries%20have%20publicly%20warned%20Pakistan%20cautioning%20that%20it%20would%20be%20consumed%20by%20its%20own%20culture%20of%20terror%20and%20violence.%20Pakistan%20will%20reap%20what%20it%20sows.%20To%20blame%20others%20for%20its%20own%20misdeeds%20can%20neither%20be%20a%20justification%20nor%20a%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Indian%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20India%20has%20not%20reacted%20to%20the%20Chinese%20statement%20yet%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20happy%20with%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%20has%20several%20times%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchina-again-puts-technical-hold-on-unsc-sanctioning-jems-rauf-azhar%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eput%20a%20hold%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20India-backed%20proposals%20to%20list%20Pakistan-based%20terrorists%20at%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%E2%80%99s%20sanctions%20committee%2C%20which%20had%20led%20New%20Delhi%20to%20accuse%20Beijing%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Funsc-india-china-blacklist-abdul-rauf-azhar%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edoublespeak%20and%20double%20standards%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20in%20fighting%20terrorism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706637035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F31140436%2Fimage-871.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fchina-on-pakistans-allegations-indian-involvement-in-killing-its-citizens%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Last%20week%2C%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20secretary%20Muhammad%20Syrus%20Sajjad%20Qazi%20had%20asserted%20that%20an%20investigation%20had%20uncovered%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%20evidence%E2%80%9D%20linking%20two%20Indian%20agents%20to%20the%20murders%20of%20two%20Pakistani%20citizens%20in%20September%20and%20October%202023.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fchina-on-pakistans-allegations-indian-involvement-in-killing-its-citizens%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Wins%20Chandigarh%20Mayoral%20Polls%20Amid%20Rigging%20Allegations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30222131%2FChandigarh-celebration.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20which%20otherwise%20is%20short%20of%20a%20simple%20majority%20in%20Chandigarh%E2%80%99s%2035-member%20municipal%20corporation%20(MC)%20house%2C%20clinched%20the%20mayoral%20polls%20on%20Tuesday%20(January%2030)%20amid%20allegations%20of%20vote%20rigging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20combined%20opposition%20of%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20jointly%20fought%20the%20election%20and%20had%20the%20requisite%20votes%20to%20win%20the%20polls%2C%20shared%20a%20video%20grab%20showing%20presiding%20officer%20Anil%20Masih%20using%20a%20pen%20on%20many%20votes%2C%20which%20they%20believed%20was%20deliberately%20done%20to%20invalidate%20some%20of%20the%20ballots%20cast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%20eight%20votes%20were%20declared%20invalid%20during%20counting%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20mayoral%20candidate%2C%20Manoj%20Sonkar%2C%20to%20win%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20also%20alleged%20that%20Masih%20also%20took%20away%20the%20cast%20ballots%20and%20later%20tore%20them%20off%2C%20something%20he%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Masih%2C%20who%20is%20a%20nominated%20councillor%20and%20is%20learnt%20to%20be%20heading%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Chandigarh%20minority%20cell%2C%20said%20that%20the%20votes%20were%20declared%20invalid%20due%20to%20councillors%E2%80%99%20own%20mischief.%20They%20did%20not%20properly%20cast%20votes%2C%20which%20made%20their%20votes%20invalid%20during%20counting%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20I%20invited%20members%20of%20the%20opposition%20to%20check%20all%20the%20votes%20after%20the%20counting%2C%20but%20they%20created%20a%20ruckus%20and%20even%20tried%20to%20snatch%20the%20votes.%20All%20thanks%20to%20Chandigarh%E2%80%99s%20police%20security%2C%20the%20votes%20were%20taken%20into%20safe%20custody.%20They%20are%20now%20with%20the%20Chandigarh%20administration%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20did%20not%20elaborate%20what%20made%20eight%20votes%20invalid%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%20that%20there%20was%20improper%20marking%20on%20the%20said%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAAP%20moves%20HC%2C%20case%20listing%20on%20Wednesday%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20allegations%20and%20counter-allegations%20were%20flying%20thick%2C%20the%20AAP%20moved%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court%20demanding%20fresh%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20case%20is%20listed%20for%20hearing%20on%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20the%20AAP%20claimed%20in%20its%20petition%20that%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20mayoral%20election%20was%20the%20result%20of%20complete%20fraud%20and%20forgery%20by%20the%20presiding%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20petition%2C%20the%20problem%20started%20when%20the%20presiding%20officer%20ordered%20the%20officials%20of%20the%20MC%20to%20empty%20the%20ballot%20box%20in%20one%20of%20the%20trays%20kept%20on%20the%20table%20and%20asked%20everyone%20to%20step%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20announced%20in%20the%20house%20that%20he%20was%20going%20to%20start%20the%20counting%20of%20the%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECouncillors%20from%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20AAP%20immediately%20raised%20the%20issue%20that%20according%20to%20the%20rules%20and%20precedents%2C%20one%20nominee%20from%20each%20party%20contesting%20the%20election%20had%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20counting%20process%20along%20with%20the%20presiding%20officer%20by%20monitoring%20the%20position%20of%20the%20votes%20cast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20petition%2C%20the%20demand%20was%20not%20accepted%20despite%20objections%20from%20the%20opposition%20and%20he%20began%20counting%20on%20his%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20three%20baskets%20in%20front%20of%20the%20presiding%20officer%2C%20one%20for%20the%20AAP%20and%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20candidate%2C%20another%20for%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20and%20a%20third%20for%20invalid%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20clear%20from%20the%20videography%20that%20the%20Presiding%20Officer%20shuffled%20the%20casted%20%5Bsic%5D%20votes%20from%20one%20basket%20to%20another%20basket%20only%20with%20a%20view%20to%20create%20a%20confusion%20during%20which%20he%20completely%20compromised%20the%20election%20process%20by%20forgery%20and%20tampering%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20petition%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20prescribed%20authority%20and%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20who%20were%20present%20were%20mute%20spectators%20and%20did%20not%20ensure%20a%20free%20and%20a%20fair%20election.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20MC%20house%20numbers%20stack%20up%20and%20what%20happened%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%2035-member%20MC%20house%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%2014%20councillors.%20The%20Congress%20has%20seven%20councillors%2C%20the%20AAP%2013%2C%20and%20one%20councillor%20belongs%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20former%20ally%2C%20the%20Akali%20Dal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20one%20additional%20vote%20of%20the%20Chandigarh%20MP%2C%20who%20is%20the%20ex-officio%20member%20of%20the%20house%3B%20currently%2C%20that%20is%20BJP%20MP%20Kirron%20Kher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20a%20maximum%20of%2015%20votes%2C%20while%20the%20joint%20opposition%20candidate%20of%20the%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20had%2020%20votes%2C%20five%20more%20than%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20tally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20election%20result%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Manoj%20Sonkar%20got%2016%20votes%2C%20while%20AAP-Congress%20candidate%20Kuldeep%20Tita%20got%20just%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20believed%20that%20eight%20votes%20of%20opposition%20members%20were%20declared%20%E2%80%9Cinvalid%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20BJP%20not%20only%20retained%20its%20tally%20but%20had%20the%20support%20of%20Akali%20councillors%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAllegations%20and%20counter-allegations%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20chief%20minister%20and%20AAP%20supremo%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20called%20the%20result%20%E2%80%9Cdishonest%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20worrying%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20these%20people%20can%20stoop%20so%20low%20in%20a%20mayor%E2%80%99s%20election%2C%20then%20they%20can%20go%20to%20any%20extent%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20Punjab%20in-charge%20and%20MP%2C%20Raghav%20Chadha%2C%20compared%20what%20had%20happened%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctreason%E2%80%9D%20and%20demanded%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20presiding%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Pawan%20Kumar%20Bansal%20too%20alleged%20that%20the%20presiding%20officer%20conducted%20a%20charade%20of%20an%20election.%20It%20was%20a%20blatant%20misuse%20of%20election%20procedure%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20members%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20the%20Congress%20which%20spoiled%20the%20party%20for%20the%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeven%20out%20of%20the%20eight%20invalid%20votes%20were%20of%20Congress%20councillors.%20They%20deliberately%20played%20mischief%20with%20their%20votes%20after%20the%20AAP%20in%20Punjab%20decided%20to%20go%20alone%20in%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandigarh%20Congress%20chief%20H.S.%20Lucky%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20this.%20He%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20covering%20up%20for%20its%20blatant%20misdeed%20in%20the%20mayoral%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20AAP%20had%20a%20pre-election%20pact%20that%20the%20AAP%20candidate%20would%20fight%20for%20the%20mayor%E2%80%99s%20post%2C%20while%20Congress%20candidates%20would%20fight%20for%20the%20senior%20deputy%20mayor%20and%20deputy%20mayor%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20BJP%20played%20fraud%20and%20snatched%20the%20victory%20in%20undemocratic%20manner%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20mayoral%20election%20was%20slated%20for%20January%2018.%20But%20the%20elections%20were%20postponed%20citing%20the%20presiding%20officer%E2%80%99s%20ill%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20to%20go%20%5Bthe%20high%20court%5D%20to%20reconvene%20the%20election%20and%20when%20it%20was%20held%20today%2C%20the%20outcome%20is%20for%20everyone%20to%20see%20how%20it%20was%20rigged%20and%20tempered.%20We%20are%20fully%20backing%20the%20AAP%20in%20its%20petition%20in%20%5Bthe%20high%20court%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706635196000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30222131%2FChandigarh-celebration.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-wins-chandigarh-mayoral-polls-amid-rigging-allegations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20has%20moved%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court%20seeking%20fresh%20polls.%20The%20presiding%20officer%20has%20denied%20allegations%20of%20rigging.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-wins-chandigarh-mayoral-polls-amid-rigging-allegations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20tells%20press%20he%20has%20decided%20on%20response%20to%20drone%20attack%20in%20Jordan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706633716000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F16DD2%2Fproduction%2F_132505639_p0h80q4p.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68146855%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20president%20spoke%20to%20press%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20adding%20he%20does%20not%20want%20a%20%26quot%3Bwider%20war%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%