%20skills.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20as%20I%20said%20earlier%2C%20one%20of%20the%20ways%20to%20do%20that%20is%20by%20teaching%20it%20%5Bconversational%20English%5D%20to%20people.%20Through%20this%2C%20you%20are%20not%20only%20helping%20people%20grow%20but%20also%20growing%20yourself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20longer%20videos%20but%20since%20people%20these%20days%20watch%20a%20lot%20of%20shorts%2C%20I%20thought%20making%20these%20reels%20was%20a%20way%20to%20earn%20a%20greater%20following.%20Since%20my%20content%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20people%20have%20been%20asking%20me%20to%20make%20longer%20videos%20on%20how%20to%20speak%20English.%20So%2C%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20develop%20a%20course%20for%20people%20which%20will%20probably%20start%20in%20a%20few%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(You%20can%20watch%20more%20of%20Dhiraj%20Takri%E2%80%99s%20content%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdhirajtakri%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Instagram%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Dhiraj%20Takri)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706622666000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D340080%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dhiraj%20Takri%2C%20a%2021-year-old%20content%20creator%20from%20rural%20Odisha%2C%20has%20become%20an%20internet%20sensation%20for%20teaching%20people%20on%20Instagram%20how%20to%20speak%20English%20like%20an%20American%20by%20incorporating%20snippets%20from%20web%20series%20and%20TV%20shows.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%202%20Brothers%2