rts%20and%20become%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F277489%2Fthe-great-gama-pehlwan-wrestling-champion-of-the-world-india-partition-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekung%20fu%E2%80%99%20master%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%2C%20I%20would%20work%20in%20the%20day%20and%20learn%20martial%20arts%20in%20the%20night.%20I%20remembered%20how%20Bruce%20Lee%20also%20worked%20in%20a%20Chinese%20restaurant%20as%20a%20dishwasher.%20My%20life%20was%20similar%20when%20I%20came%20to%20China%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20now-Xi%E2%80%99an%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20just%20five%20years%2C%20he%20went%20from%20being%20a%20waiter%20to%20a%20supervisor%20and%20then%20became%20a%20general%20manager.%20His%20unwavering%20dedication%20and%20tireless%20efforts%20are%20evident%20today%20as%20he%20proudly%20owns%20a%20thriving%20chain%20comprising%2013%20restaurants%20strategically%20located%20in%20key%20districts%20across%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20reason%20behind%20this%20progress%20was%20that%20I%20never%20believed%20in%20shortcuts%20but%20in%20consistent%20efforts.%20Today%E2%80%99s%20younger%20generations%20lack%20that.%20They%20are%20in%20a%20haste.%20I%20improved%20myself%20using%20the%20internet%20and%20through%20failed%20interviews.%20Without%20any%20hotel%20management%20degree%2C%20I%20went%20from%20earning%20Rs%2015%2C000%20to%20Rs%203.5%20lakh%20per%20month.%20Instead%20of%20working%20eight%20hours%2C%20I%20worked%2018%20hours%20to%20improve%20my%20skill%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dev%2C%20who%20owns%20the%20Amber%20Palace%20restaurant%20in%20Xi%E2%80%99an.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDev-Raturi-3-1705930952.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20a%20span%20of%20five